millions of years,

245
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,000
watching.

246
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
And not only us,

247
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,000
but others too.

248
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,000
Back in his time,

249
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,000
the great scientist,

250
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:39,000
the Russian scientist Konstantin Tsiolkovsky,

251
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:42,000
said that not even the whole universe,

252
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,000
but simply our own galaxy,

253
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
the solar system,

254
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:50,000
is teeming with different intelligent civilizations.

255
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:53,000
And until we overcome our egocentrism,

256
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,000
such contact, communication,

257
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,000
probably won't happen.

258
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,000
Official science constantly proves

259
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,000
that the only intelligent being

260
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
is the humans on this planet.

261
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
If we don't overcome this,

262
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,000
then we will never meet anyone

263
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
and will constantly remain

264
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
in these three spaces,

265
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,000
in three dimensions.

266
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:13,000
So we only know three dimensions, right?

267
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,000
But there is a fourth and a fifth.

268
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,000
While we are talking here,

269
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,000
in this beautiful place,

270
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
in the center of Tirana,

271
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
the capital of Albania,

272
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,000
maybe there are other parallel worlds too.

273
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,000
Maybe they are playing chess,

274
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,000
having a conversation.

275
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,000
And what did the spaceship look like?

276
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,000
I know you said it was big,

277
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
maybe multiple soccer fields.

278
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,000
What was the kind of architecture like?

279
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,000
And was it metal?

280
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,000
Did it look like it was from material

281
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,000
not made of this Earth?

282
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,000
I only saw it from the inside,

283
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,000
because I was immediately there.

284
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,000
It was a large space,

285
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,000
like several football fields large.

286
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:55,000
Then we walked for a while.

287
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,000
There were screens,

288
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,000
or like glass sheets.

289
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,000
But the most interesting thing I noticed,

290
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,000
when I later analyzed the whole situation,

291
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,000
was that they weren't paying attention to me at all.

292
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:07,960
they weren't paying attention to me at all, one of them was just telling me something,

293
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:13,320
and that was it, I just appeared there and it didn't matter. They were tall, dressed in these

294
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:20,120
yellow outfits, that's it, and they didn't really pay attention to me. One of them led me to a large

295
00:17:20,120 --> 00:17:26,040
porthole, like a porthole window. And the reason I realized it was a ship was because it wasn't just

296
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:32,920
hovering over Moscow, it seemed to move freely, shifting through different times, different

297
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:39,480
spaces and different dimensions. Why? Because on Earth you couldn't see anything like that.

298
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:46,680
I was looking, and there was something like a fiery… well, like a planet giving off heat.

299
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:52,360
And from there they were taking out some kind of cylinders, or maybe not cylinders, more like

300
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:59,080
boxes, they were loading those into the ship. Maybe they were collecting something, maybe

301
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:04,040
conducting experiments, maybe they had landed on some planet while I was there.

302
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,120
They might have gone down there and taken those boxes with them.

303
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:15,160
We were probably moving through space, maybe it came from the fourth dimension,

304
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:20,520
because now, according to quantum mechanics, according to quantum theory,

305
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:25,880
objects can move in a matter of seconds from one end of the universe to another.

306
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:33,000
Well, maybe it was Earth, just on the other side, maybe it was the far side of the Moon,

307
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:39,320
but on the inside it was kinda ordinary, well, like a room. They resemble us,

308
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:45,080
as I already mentioned. Tall, yellow clothing. They practically did not speak,

309
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:51,800
probably communicated thoughts to each other over a distance. I didn't feel anything unusual.

310
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:57,400
Well, it seemed like I was in some kind of laboratory, a scientific laboratory,

311
00:18:57,400 --> 00:19:02,760
or a practical laboratory. I realized it was a spaceship, because there were somewhat different

312
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:08,760
people around me. But on the other hand, perhaps they could influence the state of the mind,

313
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:15,560
so that a person wouldn't go insane immediately. Because, when I returned back to reality,

314
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:24,040
to my apartment in the city of Moscow, I felt normal. My friends were already in the apartment,

315
00:19:25,080 --> 00:19:32,120
looking for me for over an hour, and couldn't find me. And then I came out of the bedroom,

316
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:37,960
which they had entered and exited ten times already. They even called the police. Everyone

317
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:43,800
was looking for me. They arrived to pick me up at eleven in the morning. My assistant had the keys.

318
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:49,560
He opened the door, they went in, went to the kitchen to put the kettle on. Then my friend says,

319
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:55,800
we need to wake Kersan up, we have to go to the airport. The bedroom door was open,

320
00:19:55,800 --> 00:20:03,800
they go in, and I'm not there. Slippers are in place, phones are in place. They checked the bathroom

321
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:10,280
and every other room in the apartment. But well, I wasn't there. The balcony door was open, and that's

322
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:16,680
it. They went downstairs, asked the security, and he said, well, I didn't see him leave anywhere.

323
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:23,800
The building isn't very big. They checked the video cameras. No one arrived or left, no one flew out,

324
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:31,080
but the camera wasn't looking at the sky, mostly at the entrance and exit. And for a whole hour,

325
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:33,640
they were searching, wondering where I was.

326
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:39,480
Vasili, how long have you worked with Kersan Ulyumzinab?

327
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:43,160
About 40 years.

328
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:48,040
Wow, 40 years. Amazing. So very long history, you guys are very close.

329
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:53,800
What happened on the night of September 17, 1997?

330
00:20:54,360 --> 00:21:01,000
Well, that was a long time ago. The driver, a mutual friend, and I went to his apartment.

331
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:05,640
We were supposed to take him to the airport. He was flying out at one o'clock in the afternoon

332
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:12,280
that day, to Elista, which is the capital of Kalmykia. When we arrived at the house,

333
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:18,200
I called him on the phone. But he didn't answer. So I decided to go up to the apartment.

334
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:24,840
I had my own keys. I ringed the bell first. He didn't open. I unlocked the apartment with my key.

335
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:31,880
Went into one room, then another. He wasn't there. Not in the kitchen, either. Then I saw his

336
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:39,000
clothes hanging. Two mobile phones were lying on the nightstand. I was surprised. Where did he go?

337
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:47,480
So I called my friend up. I said something weird is going on. We have a situation. His things are here,

338
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:54,280
but he's nowhere to be found. Then some time passed, maybe an hour, and suddenly he appears from the

339
00:21:54,280 --> 00:22:01,880
bedroom, even though he wasn't there before. I was so surprised. Where did you come from, Kursen?

340
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:07,800
You weren't here. He laughed and said, well, aliens took me.

341
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:12,920
And after a certain time, I just came out of the bedroom and went to the bathroom.

342
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:19,160
They followed me into the bathroom and started touching me, like, are you alive or not?

343
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:28,760
I said, alive. Well, where were you? I said, I was flying with friends. They were showing me their

344
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:35,720
ship or something like that. Yes, I was in space. Well, that's interesting, they say. No, you're

345
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:42,120
probably joking. I say, no, it's true. When Kursen came back down on the ship,

346
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:49,000
or however he got back into that room, and you asked him what had happened,

347
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:55,640
he said to you, I was taken by extraterrestrials. And then at that point, did you ask a lot of

348
00:22:55,640 --> 00:23:00,920
follow-up questions? And did you learn anything about his interactions with these extraterrestrials?

349
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:08,040
I asked him, and how did you communicate with them? In what language? He said, at some subconscious level.

350
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:13,960
Interesting. And did you learn anything else about the exact communication between him

351
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:19,480
and the extraterrestrials? Did he ask them any questions and learn any interesting information

352
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:27,080
that he then relayed to you? A difficult question. Well, you see, communication probably happens

353
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:32,680
through thoughts, most likely. But he didn't tell me much. Maybe there were some secrets.

354
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:39,720
Secrets from everyone else. Because he communicated with them privately, you could say.

355
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:47,320
So why was my state normal, not surprised? Well, because I was there, probably on purpose.

356
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:52,760
They probably have this effect so that a person doesn't go crazy, so they don't take them to a

357
00:23:52,760 --> 00:24:00,680
psychiatric hospital, right? Back in 1997-98, when I talked with one of the NASA representatives,

358
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:09,160
he says, we officially record about 4000 cases a year when people notice unidentified objects,

359
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:13,480
like saucers, like saucers, and some talk about their contacts.

360
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:20,120
Well, why was I chosen? I think it's because I was supposed to say something about it.

361
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:25,000
Who did you speak to at NASA who told you about the 4000 encounters a year?

362
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:30,280
I met with many people. I can't remember all the names right now.

363
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:35,800
I have business cards, though. It was very interesting back then.

364
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:44,040
Not only with NASA, but also with other space research centers in France, Japan, China, and India.

365
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:49,560
After I mentioned that I had a contact, I received many letters and inquiries.

366
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:57,560
At that time, I was the President of the Republic of Kalmykia and the President of the World Chess

367
00:24:57,560 --> 00:25:06,280
Federation FIDE, which now includes about 200 countries. I was also a Senator and a member

368
00:25:06,280 --> 00:25:14,360
of the Parliament of the Russian Federation. I visited other countries, both officially and unofficially,

369
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:20,760
and I had many friends in the United States of America. I was friends with Henry Kissinger,

370
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:26,200
met with Jimmy Carter, and with many other presidents and representatives of NASA.

371
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:36,120
I interacted with them back then, in the 1990s. Well, for them it was a known thing, self-evident.

372
00:25:36,120 --> 00:25:43,560
And then, when we talked with the former President of the Soviet Union, Mikhail Gorbachev,

373
00:25:44,600 --> 00:25:50,200
he also spoke about the fact that there are various civilizations that have made contact with

374
00:25:50,200 --> 00:26:01,000
representatives of our Earth. Well, I'm sure you can probably just ask, just call NASA. I'm sure my

375
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:07,960
visit was registered there somehow, or maybe not. But a few people from there invited me for a friendly

376
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:13,960
lunch. When I was visiting as a member of the Russian parliament in the United States Congress,

377
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:21,560
um, I received a call. Someone introduced themselves, saying, we're from NASA,

378
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:28,760
we heard about your statement, and would like to meet. They invited me for lunch. During the lunch,

379
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:34,200
we had a friendly conversation. But it wasn't just representatives from NASA,

380
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:39,000
there were also leaders from other countries. One of the presidents of a country,

381
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:42,680
which is part of the group of seven leading countries in the world,

382
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:46,760
when I was at a dinner at his home while visiting that country,

383
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:51,480
he started asking about my contacts with them. And his wife says,

384
00:26:52,600 --> 00:26:58,520
well, you saw it too. We saw it when you were on vacation at the ocean. Tell him. He says,

385
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:05,640
am I stupid or what? I have parliamentary elections in six months. My party is running.

386
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:11,080
They'll say that the party leader, the President of the country, is a bit crazy,

387
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:17,640
the people there will never elect. I didn't say right away that I met them. I thought for a long

388
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:25,320
time about whether to say it or not. After all, at that time, in 1997, I held many official positions.

389
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:30,680
I was also the President of the Russian Chamber of Businessmen and Entrepreneurs.

390
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:39,000
So, if I declare that I, well, communicate or meet aliens on a flying saucer, how will my fellow

391
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:45,480
businessmen, friends, like Oppenheimer, or Rockefeller, Rothschild, and other businessmen

392
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:51,480
from other countries, regard me? How will senators, members of parliaments communicate with me?

393
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:54,680
How will presidents of countries look at me?

394
00:27:54,680 --> 00:28:00,840
Do you speculate as to why they took Kyrsan? Do you think it affected him in any way,

395
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:07,480
either positively or negatively? A difficult question. People are afraid to admit that they

396
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:15,560
believe in aliens, have seen aliens. You see, it takes some courage to talk about it, because it can

397
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:24,600
be interpreted in different ways. You have to understand, he held a really high position

398
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:30,040
back then. Absolutely, I agree. You understand what I'm talking about, right?

399
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:36,680
Yeah. Do you remember if the Russian government investigated the experience at all? Did they

400
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:43,800
look into it? I know Kyrsan spoke with Boris Yeltsin at the time, he also debriefed Putin. Do you know if

401
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:49,880
they looked into it at all? Well, actually, he said that he talked with Yeltsin about this story.

402
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:59,000
Whether Yeltsin reported it to Putin, I'm not aware. And did the Russian government come to you

403
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:03,640
guys at all and ask further questions about what happened, did they investigate at all,

404
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:07,240
or did they just kind of brush it off and not think twice about it?

405
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:14,840
There were some talks with journalists. You know, some close associates asked around,

406
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:26,200
government type. As a politician, you need to calculate how your action or how your decree

407
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:34,280
or regulation will affect the development of the country. So I took two sheets of paper and started

408
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:41,880
writing the cons. I always start with the cons. If tomorrow I declare to the press that I've met

409
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:49,240
with extraterrestrials or travelled on a spacecraft, what would people think? What would my business

410
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:57,240
associates say? They'd probably ask, how can we possibly conduct business with you? How could we

411
00:29:57,240 --> 00:30:03,720
entrust you with a hundred dollars? You'd just hand it over to the aliens and fly away with them. So,

412
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:10,600
just the cons list was about 10 to 20 points. Then a second sheet of paper with the pros.

413
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:16,920
If tomorrow I tell journalists and my colleagues that I met with aliens, what would that give me?

414
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:24,840
Some PR? I was already well known in the country and worldwide. I had an audience. Maybe it would bring in

415
00:30:24,840 --> 00:30:32,360
more votes. But it's the opposite. People would start talking stuff. And that is precisely what

416
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:38,520
happened. The 13th World Chess Champion, Garry Kasparov, immediately began to state,

417
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:45,560
what kind of President of the World Chess Federation can Kurson be if he has met with aliens? He must be

418
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:51,960
removed and replaced. How can he possibly lead the Chess Federation if he's mentally unstable?

419
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:58,280
The opposition, including communists and others within the Republic of Kalmykia, immediately will

420
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:04,520
declare, we absolutely must re-elect the President of the Republic. He is clearly not fit for office.

421
00:31:05,080 --> 00:31:11,000
He needs to be sent to a mental institution. He needs to be treated. So there wasn't a single pro,

422
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:17,800
really. And so I didn't mention it. I was thinking about it. And then, as if in a dream,

423
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:25,960
one night while I was sleeping I heard, what are you afraid of? Why aren't you speaking? You met with

424
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:33,640
us, didn't you? I thought, what do I have to be afraid of? Perhaps I need to take a bold step,

425
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:41,320
or a heroic deed even. Someone has to be the first to speak up. If a farmer had said it, or, you know,

426
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:48,280
a doctor, or just an ordinary labourer, they would probably say he'd had too much vodka,

427
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:54,760
or perhaps took some substances and now telling stories. So I've been thinking about it quite a bit.

428
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:59,720
What if the President say it? Or even twice the President? Because I am both the President of the

429
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:05,960
Republic and the President of Chess Federation. Then they might treat it a little differently. But still,

430
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:12,040
when I spoke about it, everyone just started laughing, mocking, and joking about it. And look,

431
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:17,400
almost 30 years have passed already, and people still don't understand. To this day,

432
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:21,880
they don't understand me. They think that they are alone in this universe and on this Earth.

433
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:27,880
Do you have any alternative explanation for what happened to Kirsan that night? Have you thought

434
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:34,360
of anything else that's possible beyond him being taken by extraterrestrials aboard a spacecraft?

435
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:39,880
Well, teleportation maybe… And you fully trust Kirsan,

436
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:45,560
he would never be dishonest with you… An honest person.

437
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:52,440
I've known him for a long time. As I said, I met him over 40 years ago.

438
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:54,680
We've been going through life together ever since.

439
00:32:54,680 --> 00:33:02,680
It was the year 97. How old was I? 35? 35 years old. And behind me, well,

440
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:08,520
I was already the President of Chalmykia. By the way, I entered the Guinness Book of Records twice,

441
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:13,960
as the youngest President in the world and as the only person who held two official positions at the

442
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:19,640
same time. President of the World Chess Federation and President of the Republic of Chalmykia.

443
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:28,360
And on top of that, I was a member of Parliament, a member of the Senate. I was also the President of

444
00:33:28,360 --> 00:33:35,480
the Russian Chamber of Entrepreneurs and an advisor to many Presidents around the world, including the

445
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:43,320
President of South Korea and the President of Mongolia. I had friends in many countries. I traveled a lot.

446
00:33:43,320 --> 00:33:50,440
One time I set a record. In a single year, I visited 108 countries.

447
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:54,600
One hundred and eight in one year. Wow. That's amazing.

448
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:59,640
And yeah, I wasn't going there as a tourist. Not to look around the city or anything like that.

449
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:06,840
I was going there to work. You arrive in the morning, meet with the President, then hold a press conference with the Prime Minister.

450
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:13,960
In the morning you're in Uruguay, by lunch you're in Paraguay, in the evening Brazil, the next day New York, Boston,

451
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:20,920
then Canada, and so on. It was non-stop. Why am I saying all this? To show that I wasn't some unstable person, right?

452
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:29,240
